:"https:\/\/www.mintpressnews.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/2015-07-10T201157Z_820063818_GF10000155529_RTRMADP_3_YEMEN-SECURITY-150x150.jpg","id":238869,"title":"Ansarullah Leader Explains How US and UN Sandbagged Yemen Peace Talks","excerpt":"The last thing Saudi Arabia and its Western allies want is a self-sustaining, economically viable, militarily strong, and anti-imperialist Yemen at the bottom of the Arabian Peninsula, controlling the Red Sea and its strategic waterways. Yemen\u2019s geographic placement in regards to the flow of world capital cannot be stressed enough.\r\n\r\n","author":"            <a href=\"https:\/\/www.mintpressnews.com\/author\/randi-nord\/\" class=\"author\">\n\t\t\t\tRandi Nord            <\/a>\n\t\t\t","url":"https:\/\/www.mintpressnews.com\/ansarullah-leader-mohammed-ali-al-houthi-on-how-us-sandbagged-yemen-peace-talks\/238869\/"},{"tag":"Drawing Palestine from Prison","default_tag":"In-depth","featured_image":"https:\/\/www.mintpressnews.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/WB_056-820x460.jpg","image":"https:\/\/www.mintpressnews.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/WB_056-150x150.jpg","id":238778,"title":"The Artwork of Palestinian Cartoonist Mohammad Sabaaneh","excerpt":"\u201cMost artists describe the Palestinian as a hero, even if imprisoned or killed by Israelis. I prefer to convey the message that Palestinians are human beings, so I portray suffering. The hero does not need anyone to stand with him -- the hero is strong -- but human beings need and demand someone to show solidarity with them.\u201d\r\n\r\n","author":"            <a href=\"https:\/\/www.mintpressnews.com\/author\/ramona-wadi\/\" class=\"author\">\n\t\t\t\tRamona Wadi            <\/a>\n\t\t\t","url":"https:\/\/www.mintpressnews.com\/the-artwork-of-palestinian-cartoonist-mohammad-sabaaneh\/238778\/"},{"tag":"Bleeding Out","default_tag":"In-depth","featured_image":"https:\/\/www.mintpressnews.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/AP_16312839823917-820x460.jpg","image":"https:\/\/www.mintpressnews.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/AP_16312839823917-150x150.jpg","id":238760,"title":"CNA and Retiring Head RoseAnn DeMoro Leave Labor in Critical Condition","excerpt":"Dubbed by many the nation\u2019s most progressive labor union the CNA in fact provides a case study in how organized labor -- the engine for creating the most prosperous working class in the known world -- finds itself at death\u2019s door at the exact moment when American workers are in dire need of advocates.\r\n\r\n","author":"            <a href=\"https:\/\/www.mintpressnews.com\/author\/jon-jeter\/\" class=\"author\">\n\t\t\t\tJon Jeter            <\/a>\n\t\t\t","url":"https:\/\/www.mintpressnews.com\/cna-head-roseann-demoro-leave-labor-unions-in-critical-condition\/238760\/"},{"tag":"Operation Juniper Cobra","default_tag":"In-depth","featured_image":"https:\/\/www.mintpressnews.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/27c961310fe766535b22706f5b985350-001-820x460.jpg","image":"https:\/\/www.mintpressnews.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/03\/27c961310fe766535b22706f5b985350-001-150x150.jpg","id":238768,"title":"US Commander: \u2018US Troops Prepared to Die for Israel\u2019 in War against Syria, Hezbollah","excerpt":"Operation Juniper Cobra is not a routine exercise; it is a portent of a potentially devastating war against Syria, Hezbollah and Gaza for which Israel is actively preparing -- a war likely to erupt within the coming months.\r\n\r\n","author":"            <a href=\"https:\/\/www.mintpressnews.com\/author\/whitney-webb\/\" class=\"author\">\n\t\t\t\tWhitney Webb            <\/a>\n\t\t\t","url":"https:\/\/www.mintpressnews.com\/israel-us-operation-juniper-cobra-a-harbinger-of-war-on-syria-hezbollah\/238768\/"}];
