        </h1>
        <h2>
			<p>Buried among statistics on gun profits and lobbying efforts is the terrifying reality of just how unique America&#8217;s gun obsession and associated violence are. And the equally terrifying plan by the NRA to “normalize” gun possession in nearly every nook and cranny of American life.</p>
